00:46.567 --> 00:48.567
Just time for a quick recap
of the week,

00:48.567 --> 00:50.533
and we begin with
the continuing investigation

00:50.533 --> 00:53.367
of Donald Trump and Russia,
a scandal that we've been

00:53.367 --> 00:55.734
referring to as
"Stupid Watergate,"

00:55.734 --> 00:58.533
because it has all the potential
consequences of Watergate,

00:58.533 --> 01:01.900
