would stop dating.

02:12.367 --> 02:14.700
For instance, why did he make
such a big show

02:14.700 --> 02:16.633
of racing to the White House
to share his information

02:16.633 --> 02:17.734
with President Trump,

02:17.734 --> 02:19.934
especially in light
of this revelation?

02:19.934 --> 02:22.300
- "The New York Times"
reported White House officials

02:22.300 --> 02:24.266
were the source
of intelligence reports

02:24.266 --> 02:26.834
given to House Intelligence
Chair Devin Nunes.

02:26.834 --> 02:29.233
- Okay, so to recap.

02:29.233 --> 02:31.600
Devin took what appears to be
an unnecessary trip

02:31.600 --> 02:33.633
to tell what appears to be
unimportant news

02:33.633 --> 02:36.734
to what may have been
the source of the news itself.

02:36.734 --> 02:38.934
So what Nunes brought to light
has turned out to be

02:38.934 --> 02:40.500
a bunch of smoke and mirrors

02:40.500 --> 02:42.300
as convoluted
as it is pointless.

02:42.300 --> 02:45.900
Truly, it is the
"Now You See Me" of revelations.

02:45.900 --> 02:48.033
But wait, wait,
because Stupid Watergate

02:48.033 --> 02:50.333
found a way to get
even stupider,

02:50.333 --> 02:52.467
because the surveillance
Nunes was studying

02:52.467 --> 02:53.900
concerned the Trump
transition team,

02:53.900 --> 02:56.467
of which one member was,
yeah, you guessed it,

02:56.467 --> 02:58.934
Devin fucking Nunes.

02:58.934 --> 03:01.633
Which seems like a pretty clear
conflict of interest.

03:01.633 --> 03:03.600
So it was important for
Republicans to make clear

03:03.600 --> 03:06.900
