03:18.533 --> 03:19.867
- No!

03:19.867 --> 03:22.467
No, You absolutely do not!

03:22.467 --> 03:25.800
You do one of them
and explicitly not the other.

03:25.800 --> 03:29.233
That is literally
the whole point of Congress.

03:29.233 --> 03:32.800
And that is why this story
is Stupid Watergate.

03:32.800 --> 03:34.934
It could very
well take down the government,

03:34.934 --> 03:38.300
but nobody involved understands
why, or how to cover it up,

03:38.300 --> 03:40.166
or what the government
fucking is,

03:40.166 --> 03:41.633
or possibly how to breathe

03:41.633 --> 03:44.100
