on the way,

21:13.567 --> 21:16.200
stop flying, and spend
the whole night giggling

21:16.200 --> 21:20.467
about how owls seem like
they have glasses but, like,

21:20.467 --> 21:22.834
don't have glasses.

21:22.834 --> 21:26.000
And that's crazy, right?

21:26.000 --> 21:29.600
They don't know,
but it's there, right?

21:31.734 --> 21:34.567
The point is,
if you live in Kentucky,

21:34.567 --> 21:37.166
despite there being a law
that ostensibly gives access

21:37.166 --> 21:39.700
to medical marijuana,
there's virtually no legal way

21:39.700 --> 21:40.800
for you to get it.

21:40.800 --> 21:43.100
Now, things
fractionally improved

21:43.100 --> 21:44.900
