26:19.834 --> 26:21.133
And at the end of that piece,

26:21.133 --> 26:23.266
we made the case
that adding zebras to things

26:23.266 --> 26:24.967
is always an improvement.

26:24.967 --> 26:28.066
We even uploaded
23 minutes of zebra footage

26:28.066 --> 26:30.767
so you could add zebras
to whatever you wanted.

26:30.767 --> 26:32.233
And let me just say,

26:32.233 --> 26:35.533
you people
really came through for us.

26:35.533 --> 26:37.266
To give you just a flavor.

26:37.266 --> 26:40.066
You took Mariah Carey's
New Year's Eve disaster

26:40.066 --> 26:42.700
and vastly improved it
with zebras,

26:42.700 --> 26:46.400
you completely filled the White
House Press room with them,

26:46.400 --> 26:47.867
and you put zebras into movies,

26:47.867 --> 26:49.333
like "The Shining,"

26:49.333 --> 26:51.166
"Mad Max: Fury Road,"

26:51.166 --> 26:53.233
and naturally,
"Basic Instinct".

27:01.433 --> 27:02.900
- It's nice.

27:02.900 --> 27:05.200
- Thank you so much

27:05.200 --> 27:08.266
for wasting so much
of your time with us.

27:08.266 --> 27:09.667
The point of this

27:09.667 --> 27:11.500
was to make painful moments
easier to swallow.

27:11.500 --> 27:14.033
That's why we put a zebra
into Trump's inauguration.

27:14.033 --> 27:17.500
Well, someone took that to the
next logical step.

27:17.500 --> 27:19.867
'Cause remember Trump
riding the escalator

27:19.867 --> 27:21.233
to announce his candidacy?

27:21.233 --> 27:23.700
It's a pretty horrible memory,
right?

27:23.700 --> 27:26.667
Well, get ready
to have it slightly improved.

27:26.667 --> 27:30.200
- ♪ With your baby in hand ♪

27:30.200 --> 27:33.567
♪ And an old street light ♪

27:33.567 --> 27:35.133
- It's better now.

27:35.133 --> 27:37.133
That doesn't fundamentally
change anything,

27:37.133 --> 27:39.633
but it is just better now.

27:39.633 --> 27:41.734
Now interestingly,
adding zebras turns out

27:41.734 --> 27:44.033
to make great moments
even greater as well,

27:44.033 --> 27:46.800
like this one.

27:46.800 --> 27:48.500
- Good evening.

27:48.500 --> 27:53.066
Tonight I can report to the
American people and to the world

27:53.066 --> 27:55.433
that the United States
has conducted an operation

27:55.433 --> 27:59.266
that killed Osama bin Laden,
the leader of al-Qaeda.

27:59.266 --> 28:00.600
- Yeah.

28:00.600 --> 28:03.967
And that's what I
will always remember now.

28:03.967 --> 28:06.934
But perhaps the most exciting
thing was the response

28:06.934 --> 28:09.333
to our piece
in Bolivia itself.

28:09.333 --> 28:10.767
translator: I saw it live.

28:10.767 --> 28:12.734
I was watching it on Sunday,
"Last Week Tonight,"

28:12.734 --> 28:14.100
John Oliver's program.

28:14.100 --> 28:16.233
And suddenly he starts
talking about the zebras.

28:16.233 --> 28:17.734
I thought he was only
going to comment,

28:17.734 --> 28:19.567
and suddenly he keeps talking
and talking.

28:19.567 --> 28:22.567
He keeps talking.

28:22.567 --> 28:24.633
- "I thought he was only
going to comment,

28:24.633 --> 28:26.400
"and suddenly
he keeps talking and talking.

28:26.400 --> 28:27.700
He keeps talking."

28:27.700 --> 28:31.066
That is an entirely fair
description of this show.

28:31.066 --> 28:32.900
And it actually gets
one step better,

28:32.900 --> 28:36.633
because the cebritas themselves
issued a public message.

28:36.633 --> 28:38.533
- [speaking Spanish]

28:38.533 --> 28:40.400
translator: John Oliver,
we want to invite you

28:40.400 --> 28:43.500
to La Paz, Bolivia,
to be a zebra for one day.

28:43.500 --> 28:48.300
The mayor of our Wonder City,
Luis Revilla, agrees.

28:48.300 --> 28:51.834
The 265 zebras
are waiting in La Paz.

28:51.834 --> 28:54.834
- Now, I know it's
a friendly invitation,

28:54.834 --> 28:57.166
but honestly there is
no world in which the phrase

28:57.166 --> 29:00.233
"265 zebras are waiting
for you in La Paz"

29:00.233 --> 29:03.333
does not sound
like a genuine threat.

29:03.333 --> 29:05.900
But it's true, I have been
invited to be a zebra,

29:05.900 --> 29:08.500
and sadly, I'm not going to be
able to do that anytime soon,

29:08.500 --> 29:09.867
'cause I have to be here.

29:09.867 --> 29:12.200
So this is really
a very disappointing moment

29:12.200 --> 29:15.667
for both myself
and the nation of Bolivia.

29:15.667 --> 29:18.400
But as I think
we both now know,

29:18.400 --> 29:21.200
there is a real way
to improve moments like this.

29:21.200 --> 29:22.400
Hit!

29:22.400 --> 29:23.700
[upbeat music]

29:23.700 --> 29:24.767
It's better now!

29:24.767 --> 29:26.200
That's our show!

29:26.200 --> 29:28.433
Thank you so much
for watching us.

29:28.433 --> 29:29.967
Good night!

29:29.967 --> 29:36.900
♪ ♪
